title: Amazing Spider-man: Dark Web Omnibus
description: Pryor have had enough and are reigniting the INFERNO! Spider-Man and the X-Men are not ready for what's coming, and what role does Venom have in all of this? The sun is setting, dusk is approaching, and it's going to be a long night. Plus, Spidey and Woverine team-up! Spider-Man faces judgement by a Celestial! The Hobgoblin returns and more! Collecting: Amazing Spider-Man (2022) #9-18, Free Comic Book Day (2022) Spider-Man/Venom #1, Dark Web (2023) #1 and Dark Web Finale (2023) #1
summary: The Spider-Man and X-Men crossover event of the year! The two most famous clones ever are back to take what's theirs. Ben Reilly and Madelyne
